description: Oh My Gogi! Is a food truck that will be serving Korean BBQ/Mexican Fusion food in the Houston area lunch, dinner and late night!“Gogi” in Korean means “meat” and “Oh My Gogi!” is what you’ll be saying after you try our food! The menu’s backbone will focus on our delicious Korean BBQ meat and tofu marinades combined with some of your favorite Mexican street foods.  Our marinades and salsas are homemade and our ingredients are always fresh!
name: Oh My Gogi!
